{
  "stem": "1918.5",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 344.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In the end, 30 people in that area did survive.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Those who hid in the straw.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The four of us couldn't bear the smell of boiled potatoes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We came out, and we lined up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And by the time it reached us, there were no potatoes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But were back.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were the prisoners of Hitler again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And those unconsumed potatoes that we never got cost us another sister.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because had we stayed there, there would've been four sisters alive today.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But we couldn't bear the hunger, and we didn't know what it was all about.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we came out of our hiding place, and we were back in the line of marchers.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this was now Tuesday morning.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we marched until mid day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then three girls in back of us escaped.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we always march five in a row.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "In the middle of the road, the snowy road, my sister Regina had one wooden shoe and one [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And she was coughing so badly that no matter who gave her-- somebody would have to die because one would have to go one foot shoeless.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And-- Regina-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] we lined-- Yeah, it was Tuesday morning, and we were marching.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The-- and-- and the three girls escape.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the five in the row.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And on both sides are Nazis, and in the front and in the back.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We reached a village called [NON-ENGLISH], a little German village.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And my sister Chica, who was at this end of the line, noticed that there is no smoke coming on.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "There was no central heating.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It was a little blacksmith's house, as later learned.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And there was no smoke coming out, so nobody is there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Therefore, she targeted that as the house to escape to.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
